  <section class="grid intro">
    <div class="grid-cell grid8 intro__text">
      <div class="top-content" style="color: <%= pageData.current.color %>">
        <p>CGU required a fresh appraoch to their email communications, allowing for more personalised, 1-to-1 communications with both customers and brokers.</p>
        <p>I designed a series of email templates for the Salesforce Marketing Cloud platform that would be easy to use and flexible for marketers, with no HTML knowledge required.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
    <div class="grid-cell grid4 credits">
      <h3>Design, Coding, Deployment</h3>
      <p>Rob Thwaites</p>

    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="grid">
